d Otonobe|lt=Otonobe|ja|オオトノヂ・オオトノベ}}|大斗乃弁神}} | {{nihongo|Ōtonoji|大戸之道尊, Ōtonoji-no-mikoto; 大戸摩彦尊, Ōtoma-hiko-no-mikoto; 大富道尊, Ōtomuji-no-mikoto}} and {{nihongo|Ōtomabe|大苫辺尊, Ōtomabe-no-mikoto}} |- | 6 | {{nihongo|{{Interlanguage link|Omodaru and Ayakashikone|lt=Omodaru|ja|オモダル・アヤカシコネ}}|淤母陀琉神, Omodaru-no-kami}} and {{nihongo|{{Interlanguage link|Omodaru and Ayakashikone|lt=Aya-kashiko-ne|ja|オモダル・アヤカシコネ}}|阿夜訶志古泥神, Aya-kashiko-ne-no-kami}} | {{nihongo|Omodaru|面足尊, Omodaru-no-mikoto}} and {{nihongo|Kashiko-ne|惶根尊, Kashiko-ne-no-mikoto}} |- | 7 | {{nihongo|[[Izanagi]]|伊邪那岐神, Izanagi-no-kami}} and {{nihongo|[[Izanami]]|伊邪那美神, Izanami-no-kami}} | {{nihongo|[[Izanagi]]|伊弉諾尊, Izanagi-no-mikoto}} and {{nihongo|[[Izanami]]|伊弉冉尊, Izanami-no-mikoto}} |} ==Genealogy== {{Seven Generations of Kami}}
